    <item>
      <title>安大略省福特汽车公司为应对关税措施撤回美国酒精饮料销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/ontario-s-ford-pulls-us-alcohol-from-shelves-in-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大的省份表示，将从其政府经营的酒类商店中撤下美国产品，作为对特朗普总统对加拿大进口产品征收 25% 关税的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/ontario-s-ford-pulls-us-alcohol-from-shelves-in-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 14:40:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟警告美国，若特朗普对进口商品征收关税，欧盟将予以报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/eu-warns-us-it-will-retaliate-if-trump-imposes-tariffs-on-goods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟表示，如果美国对欧盟征收关税，欧盟将“坚决回应”。这是欧盟对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的贸易策略在全球引发反响的最新不满迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/eu-warns-us-it-will-retaliate-if-trump-imposes-tariffs-on-goods</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 14:34:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据路透社报道，美国证券交易委员会工作人员被要求寻求批准启动调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/sec-staff-told-to-seek-approval-to-start-probes-reuters-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社援引知情人士透露，美国证券交易委员会工作人员已被告知在正式开始调查之前必须征得领导层的许可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/sec-staff-told-to-seek-approval-to-start-probes-reuters-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对中国征收 10% 关税后，习近平考虑采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发动新一轮贸易战后，加拿大和墨西哥领导人迅速作出回应，而中国国家主席习近平则在宣布具体反击措施之前稍事休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚政府支持酷刑受害者要求国际刑事法院采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/kenyan-victims-of-alleged-state-backed-torture-demand-icc-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群声称自己是肯尼亚政府支持的绑架事件的受害者，要求国际刑事法院对威廉·鲁托总统的政府是否侵犯人权进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/kenyan-victims-of-alleged-state-backed-torture-demand-icc-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:23:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税闪电战可能会使从牛油果到汽车等产品变得更加昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-s-new-tariff-blitz-to-hit-avocados-cars-and-bell-peppers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普即将对来自加拿大和墨西哥的商品征收 25% 的关税，并对来自中国的产品征收 10% 的关税，这一举措将对美国家庭产生影响，导致蔬菜、水果和汽车等多种商品的价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-s-new-tariff-blitz-to-hit-avocados-cars-and-bell-peppers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚总统首次出访利雅得会见 MBS</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/syria-s-interim-president-in-saudi-arabia-on-first-foreign-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚临时总统艾哈迈德·沙拉在利雅得与沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼就两国广泛的经济合作举行会谈，叙利亚新领导人希望在其首次正式出访期间获得沙特的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/syria-s-interim-president-in-saudi-arabia-on-first-foreign-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 10:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度经济增长放缓，莫迪青睐中产阶级而非失业者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/modi-favors-middle-class-over-jobless-as-india-s-growth-stumbles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了缓解全球经济面临的不利影响，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在预算中为印度中产阶级提供了大幅减税，但几乎没有为去年投票反对他的数百万失业者提供直接支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/modi-favors-middle-class-over-jobless-as-india-s-growth-stumbles</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 05:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲巨型电缆成为日益紧张的根源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/europe-s-network-of-giant-power-cables-is-becoming-political</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周挪威政府的垮台使人们关注欧洲跨境输电的数百条电缆如何被转变为政治武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/europe-s-network-of-giant-power-cables-is-becoming-political</guid>
